(ii). This is obvious for PCPC(ii), and
PCPC(iii) only has to hold for (ordinary) inside critical peaks which is guaranteed
again by CPC
HT
(ii).
Finally, let us briey discuss related work and possible extensions of our approach. First
of all, it seems rather straightforward to generalize our approach to a `commutation
setting' analogous to the one of Toyama ([Toy88]) mentioned above for Theorem 3.7.
Furthermore, we would like to mention one possible source of renements for Theorem
